Description.20: User's email account is locked due to multiple incorrect password attempts. Requires password reset and account unlock.
Description.21: Network printer is not connecting to the office network, making it impossible for employees to print documents.
Description.22: VPN connection is frequently dropping, causing remote work disruptions. User needs a stable VPN connection.
Description.23: Error encountered during the installation of a critical software update. Installation process fails with an error code.
Description.24: User's computer is experiencing significant slowdowns, especially when running multiple applications. Might require performance diagnosis.
Description.25: User is unable to access the shared network drive. Possible permission issues or network connectivity problems.
Description.26: The office Wi-Fi network keeps disconnecting, affecting multiple employees. Could be an issue with the Wi-Fi router or network configuration.
Description.27: User's PC shows a blue screen error after startup. Requires troubleshooting to identify the cause of the system crash.
Description.28: User accidentally deleted important files and needs to recover them. Possible data recovery from backups or undoing deletion.
Description.29: User's laptop battery is not charging when plugged in. Potential hardware issue with the battery or charging port.
